review.reviewBody: the beef dip is incredible!!! absolutely delicious food and my boys loved the shrimp pesto pizza Pesto Shrimp Beef Dip Breaded Chicken Tenders
They forgot the bacon on my bacon cheeseburger. And I asked for no cheese but they put cheese on it.
I ordered Nachos with spicey beef, no Spicey Beef. I ordered Chicken Burger with onion rings, was changed for those and received a wrap instead of the burger with rings.
I ordered the $13  "Deluxe" Grilled Cheese and it was tiny. the salad was good though.
I got the baked Mac and cheese and the poutine and the portion sizes were awesome and the food is delicious
